To install, move the 'Rhythmbox-Random-Album-Player' to
$HOME$/.gnome2/rhythmbox/plugins

if that directory does not exist, run the following:
mkdir -p $HOME/.gnome2/rhythmbox/plugins
mv Rhythmbox-Random-Album-Player $HOME/.gnome2/rhythmbox/plugins

Then in Rhythmbox go to Edit -> plugins and enable the 'Random Album' Plugin

Enjoy!
